In this release we’re adding RA Tickets Resale, our industry-leading resale service that lets you securely buy and sell unwanted tickets to sold-out events. Just head to the ticket page and click the ‘resell’ button. We’ve also made some huge improvements to the checkout process. You can now securely save your card details in the RA Guide, meaning you can buy tickets faster than ever.

For more info on RA Tickets Resale, head here: https://www.residentadvisor.net/tickets/resale

You can now add your RA tickets to Apple Wallet. Users from Belgium and the Netherlands can now purchase tickets using their favourite local payment methods, Bancontact and iDEAL.

1.8.8
